We need to assess if the formula in determining the value of the right can be written as the formula stated below: 


$$\begin{aligned}
\text{Value of a right}&={\text{P}_{RO}}{{- P}_{X}}
= \dfrac{{\text{(P}_{RO}}{\text{- P}_{S}{)}}}{\text{(N + 1)}}
\end{aligned}$$ 

Where:

$${\text{P}_{RO}} = {\text{Rights-on price}} \\

{\text{P}_{X}} = {\text{Ex-rights price}} \\
{\text{P}_{S}} = {\text{Subscription price}} \\
{\text{N}} = {\text{Rights needed}} \\
